# Prisma Migration Rules

- NEVER use `prisma db push` (or `prisma db push --force-reset`) for schema changes.
- For any change to `prisma/schema.prisma`:
  1. Edit `schema.prisma`
  2. Run `npx prisma migrate dev --name <migration_name>` (creates migration + applies + regenerates client)
  3. If needed, update seed and run `npm run db:seed --workspace @superboard/api`
- For CI/prod apply pending migrations only: `npx prisma migrate deploy`.
- To fully reset (dev only): `npx prisma migrate reset --force` (includes all migrations + seed).

